facebook

Class FacebookPost

  • java.lang.Object
    • socialmedia.Post<FacebookUser>
      • facebook.FacebookPost

  • public class FacebookPost
extends Post<FacebookUser>
    The FacebookPost class extends the post class and adds content that only facebook uses for their posts. FacebookPost uses types from facebook4j: Post.Property and Place.
    See Also:
    Post, Place, Post.Property
